<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mom.</b></font>

183
00:20:06,143 --> 00:20:08,983
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you still the Daoming Feng I know?</b></font>

184
00:20:13,423 --> 00:20:17,103
<font color="#ffff00"><b>An old woman like me can still learn
and grow to be a better person.</b></font>

185
00:20:33,303 --> 00:20:35,623
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mother looks really cool.</b></font>

186
00:20:41,503 --> 00:20:47,143
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I believe that a lot of people
want to be like Mrs. Daoming.</i></b></font>

187
00:20:48,783 --> 00:20:51,103
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Being in her shoes is not easy.</i></b></font>

188
00:20:51,943 --> 00:20:55,983
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>She has sacrificed a lot
to be where she is today.</i></b></font>

189
00:21:07,143 --> 00:21:09,583
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>And I, this ordinary girl,</i></b></font>

190
00:21:10,663 --> 00:21:12,303
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>am now able to start</i></b></font>

191
00:21:13,063 --> 00:21:16,223
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>this life that I've dreamed about.</i></b></font>

192
00:22:35,783 --> 00:22:36,743
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

193
00:22:37,503 --> 00:22:38,343
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

194
00:22:38,423 --> 00:22:39,743
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Don't move.
-Don't do it.</b></font>

195
00:22:42,863 --> 00:22:43,703
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop moving.</b></font>

196
00:22:49,503 --> 00:22:50,383
<font color="#ffff00"><b>WIFE</b></font>

197
00:22:50,463 --> 00:22:51,583
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What the hell is this?</b></font>

198
00:22:52,143 --> 00:22:54,583
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm marking my property.
You should go out like this tomorrow.</b></font>

199
00:22:56,583 --> 00:22:57,543
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you think I'm stupid?</b></font>

200
00:22:58,503 --> 00:22:59,583
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course you are.</b></font>

201
00:22:59,703 --> 00:23:01,223
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why would you marry me if you weren't?</b></font>

202
00:23:02,583 --> 00:23:04,103
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's enough.</b></font>

203
00:23:04,223 --> 00:23:05,783
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Now, I'll make Shancai beautiful again.</b></font>

204
00:23:09,263 --> 00:23:11,583
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I don't think you can do it.
-Does it work like this?</b></font>

205
00:23:12,263 --> 00:23:15,583
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Like this? Is this right?
-No!</b></font>

206
00:23:16,063 --> 00:23:17,063
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is this right?</b></font>

207
00:23:17,823 --> 00:23:20,623
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm going to make you beautiful too.</b></font>

208
00:23:21,743 --> 00:23:22,663
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here.</b></font>

209
00:23:24,103 --> 00:23:26,583
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right, that's enough.
I'm already beautiful.</b></font>

210
00:23:26,663 --> 00:23:28,143
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Not enough. Let's put some more on.</b></font>

211
00:23:28,663 --> 00:23:30,463
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you really going to wash my hair?</b></font>

212
00:23:30,543 --> 00:23:33,543
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm warning you. I won't put up with it.</b></font>

213
00:23:33,623 --> 00:23:34,743
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't mess around with me.</b></font>

214
00:23:36,823 --> 00:23:40,103
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm the dandruff eliminator.
I'm not afraid of you.</b></font>

215
00:23:41,223 --> 00:23:44,383
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Get in.
