216
00:23:58,383 --> 00:23:59,223
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

217
00:23:59,943 --> 00:24:01,863
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's all right. You don't need to do this.</b></font>

218
00:24:02,223 --> 00:24:03,303
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

219
00:24:03,503 --> 00:24:06,183
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Today, we're married for three months.</b></font>

220
00:24:06,303 --> 00:24:10,663
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's no greater gift that can beat
a home-cooked meal made by your husband.</b></font>

221
00:24:11,223 --> 00:24:12,383
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I understand.</b></font>

222
00:24:12,863 --> 00:24:15,023
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But it's just three months.</b></font>

223
00:24:15,503 --> 00:24:17,823
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can't we go to a restaurant like we did</b></font>

224
00:24:18,303 --> 00:24:20,383
<font color="#ffff00"><b>for our first and second
