225
00:24:21,223 --> 00:24:24,303
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Rejecting your husband's love is a crime.</b></font>

226
00:24:25,583 --> 00:24:26,543
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Get out of the way now.</b></font>

227
00:24:27,263 --> 00:24:29,863
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just wait and see.
