231
00:24:42,983 --> 00:24:44,463
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How did it grow out again?</b></font>

232
00:24:51,103 --> 00:24:52,983
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't play a prank like that again.</b></font>

233
00:24:54,263 --> 00:24:55,143
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Fine.</b></font>

234
00:24:56,623 --> 00:24:59,183
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I apologize. I'm sorry.</b></font>

235
00:24:59,263 --> 00:25:01,703
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If apologies worked,
why would we need the police?</b></font>

236
00:25:52,903 --> 00:25:53,863
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you reading?</b></font>

237
00:25:54,223 --> 00:25:56,143
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-A comic book.
-What comic book?</b></font>

238
00:25:56,663 --> 00:25:58,543
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>My Quarter of a Boyfriend.</i></b></font>

239
00:26:02,783 --> 00:26:05,463
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They look kind of like F4.</b></font>

240
00:26:06,983 --> 00:26:08,023
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But...</b></font>

241
00:26:08,663 --> 00:26:09,663
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm more handsome.</b></font>

242
00:26:10,583 --> 00:26:11,983
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes. You're more handsome.</b></font>

