<font color="#ffff00"><b>What a great idea.</b></font>

250
00:28:22,663 --> 00:28:23,783
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you kidding me?</b></font>

251
00:28:23,983 --> 00:28:27,063
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's New Year's Eve,
