<font color="#ffff00"><b>I made plans with Xiaoyou.</b></font>

254
00:28:36,423 --> 00:28:37,343
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Bye.</b></font>

255
00:28:41,663 --> 00:28:43,023
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you think I don't have plans?</b></font>

256
00:28:45,703 --> 00:28:47,343
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just have to wait longer.</b></font>

257
00:29:14,343 --> 00:29:16,583
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Look, a meteor shower.
