278
00:35:25,583 --> 00:35:27,383
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've been singing here for over a decade.</b></font>

279
00:35:27,463 --> 00:35:28,663
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've never seen you before.</b></font>

280
00:35:28,743 --> 00:35:31,103
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Yeah.
